calc_diff <- function(x){
  return(data.frame(div_u = x$div[x$fert == 0],
                    div_f = x$div[x$fert == 1],
                    diff = x$div[x$fert == 0] - x$div[x$fert == 1],
                    diff_frac = (x$div[x$fert == 0] - x$div[x$fert == 1]) / x$div[x$fert == 0] ))
  
}
